Quotations.ab:
"There are seven ratu in the hāuuani-performance, where one spreads the barəsman: the first is  
                yeŋ́hē mē aṣ̌āt̰ hacā (VrS11.30); the second, the Ahuna Vairiias (likely Y13.7);  the third, dāidī mōi (Y18.1); 
                the fourth, the Uštauuaitī or the Spəṇtā.mainiiū Gāθā;  the fifth, yeŋ́hē mē aṣ̌āt̰ hacā (Y63.1); the sixth, dāidī mōi (Y65.15); 
                the seventh, the Uštauuaitī or the Spəṇtā.mainiiū Gāθā."
